osis and treatment selection.  An MRI chest may be considered to further refine surgical planning if resection is deemed feasible.  The patient\u2019s comorbidities (diabetes and hypertension) should be considered during treatment planning.  This report is based on the available imaging data and clinical information provided; further clinical information may modify the staging or treatment recommendations.",
